  "detailed_description": "Join Benny and his friends on their journey through 5 different worlds, collecting gems, solving puzzles, and dodging sharp spikes. With 50 levels in the base game and the ability to create and share custom levels, the possibilities are endless.<br><br>Each world adds a new and game changing mechanic shown here:<br><br>World 1 introduces the dangerous spikes:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956480/extras/c1771ba1a8e0e77ca1ab2906b3ca23ba.poster.avif?t=1719438514\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956480/extras/c1771ba1a8e0e77ca1ab2906b3ca23ba.webm?t=1719438514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956480/extras/c1771ba1a8e0e77ca1ab2906b3ca23ba.mp4?t=1719438514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>World 2 introduces the weak, breakable walls:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956480/extras/fdb301c5950d2afe140b46af8368b048.poster.avif?t=1719438514\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956480/extras/fdb301c5950d2afe140b46af8368b048.webm?t=1719438514\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956480/extras/fdb301c5950d2afe140b46af8368b048.mp4?t=1719438514\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>World 3 introduces the portals:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956480/extras/e7d3f83aaf691a066c258e08336c9941.poster.avif?t=1719438514\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"